On Nov 7, 2023, two tables were created. The first was with the average critic score for Sports games in a column “sports_critic_score”. The second was with thee average critic score for Shooter games in a column called “shooter_critic_score”. Three tables were created (average, min, max) for the global_sales for: all games, Spots games, Shooter games. The data was stored in columns “average_global_sales”, “min_global_sales”, and “max_global_sales” accordingly. Two tables were created global_sales and count of games with that global_sales for: Sports games and Shooter games - columns “global_sales” and “count”.
